{"tid":667815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕毋忘報道　問「影唔影到手銬」","createTime":"2018-05-17T05:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T11:08:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"10e6196f41f914c0d66e3fef8b59374b09aedbdc","tid":667815,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180517/20393296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F20393296&d=c28YW418mKV8lj%2FngD5pW7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=f62cce13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F20393296&h=f37a1608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180517/20393296</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月17日 <br />\n<br />\n被捕毋忘報道　問「影唔影到手銬」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180517/large/17la1p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180517%2Flarge%2F17la1p6.jpg&h=131c2fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■now攝記被押走時故意停留，讓同事拍攝他雙手被手銬鎖上的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【特寫】<br />\n<br />\n在北京遭公安拘押的now新聞台攝影記者，受到暴力對待時仍堅持採訪，大叫同行記者用手機拍攝他的被捕過程，被帶上警車時又故意轉身及停留，讓同事拍攝其傷勢及雙手被手銬鎖上等情況。香港攝影記者協會則發表聲明，對記者被捕及受傷表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強行轉身展示傷勢<br />\n<br />\n據現場其他記者拍攝的片段，now新聞台攝記徐駿銘被3名便衣公安按在地上，手上攝影機亦不知所終，混亂中他大叫同事「攞手機嚟影」。<br />\n<br />\n其後徐雙手被手銬反鎖在背後，由兩名便衣左右挾持帶上警車，他高聲投訴攝影機被損壞，又一度強行轉身大叫「影我個樣」，讓人拍到其前額受傷流血。他走到警車前故意停留，多次高聲問：「影唔影到手銬？」直至同事確認已拍到，他終被強行推入警車。<br />\n<br />\n香港攝影記者協會發表聲明，指得悉一名now攝影記者採訪北京律師協會聽證會時遭警察阻撓，攝影師被多名便衣警員按在地鎖上手銬並押上警車帶走，其間攝影師額頭受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n709維權律師聽證會公安圍毆港記者叉頸按地打到爆缸　林鄭拒譴責議員斥軟弱<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n港府圖為京開脫　建制阻立會討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港府圖為京開脫　建制阻立會討論<br />\n<br />\n聽證會不准律師旁聽　剝奪自辯機會謝燕益與妻被扣6小時<br />\n<br />\n709大抓捕　王全璋生死未卜<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹：暴力程度30多年來罕見<br />\n<br />\n709維權律師聽證會　公安圍毆港記者　叉頸按地打到爆缸林鄭拒譴責　議員斥軟弱"},{"pid":"35749a0bbf3fdc3a0e4424865f817a2dc01d13f6","tid":667815,"uid":182927,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"影好啲證據，費事一陣又死無對證"},{"pid":"cc78fed73f873c8b178f0e54d3688e7769ccfee0","tid":667815,"uid":19501,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"now呢啲就真係攝影記者啦"},{"pid":"e722532770652eedd2541d6165d765cd1c5091ee","tid":667815,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"比高層問你又唔係人心入面條蟲就唔好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622abef7d19c6661ddc330653d59320c83a7768f","tid":667815,"uid":189,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"好撚Pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611eff4e0a51bb5d6e7763766b12663963736d3b","tid":667815,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a52aeaf299820bbc57b01eb68959f46db6b5b6ff","tid":667815,"uid":10334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d61050ec5c466b8d5b3137e2296b72564efa5a","tid":667815,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"有冇